text: Phai Phongsathon (Thai: ไผ่ พงศธร) (born 12 June 1982) is a Luk thung and Mor lam singer from Isan area. He also plays professional football as a midfielder for Yasothon. ==References== Category:1982 births Category:Living people Category:Thai actors Category:Thai singers Category:Thai footballers
title: Phai Phongsathon
